Il cuore visivo dello smartwatch è un ampio display AMOLED da 1,5 pollici con luminosità fino a 2000 nits, protetto da vetro Gorilla Glass 3, che assicura una perfetta visibilità anche sotto la luce diretta del sole o negli ambienti più scuri. La batteria di grande capacità permette fino a 21 giorni di autonomia.
<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1431549" title="macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-scaled.jpeg" alt="macitynet.it" width="2560" height="2560" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-scaled.jpeg 2560w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-480x480.jpeg 480w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-1200x1200.jpeg 1200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-360x360.jpeg 360w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-1536x1536.jpeg 1536w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-2048x2048.jpeg 2048w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-420x420.jpeg 420w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-696x696.jpeg 696w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-1068x1068.jpeg 1068w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-1920x1920.jpeg 1920w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-50x50.jpeg 50w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-75x75.jpeg 75w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-100x100.jpeg 100w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-200x200.jpeg 200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-front-500x500.jpeg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" />
Per gli appassionati di corsa, Balance 2 XT offre un sistema GPS preciso grazie al posizionamento satellitare a doppia banda con supporto a sei sistemi GNSS, inclusi GPS e Galileo. In più, l’orologio consente di scaricare mappe urbane, topografiche e outdoor. Il tuto è supportato dalle misurazioni del battito cardiaco e VO₂ max per ottimizzare le performance e gestire al meglio il recupero post-allenamento.
<img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1431550" title="macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-scaled.jpeg" alt="macitynet.it" width="2560" height="2560" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-scaled.jpeg 2560w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-480x480.jpeg 480w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-1200x1200.jpeg 1200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-360x360.jpeg 360w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-1536x1536.jpeg 1536w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-2048x2048.jpeg 2048w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-420x420.jpeg 420w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-696x696.jpeg 696w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-1068x1068.jpeg 1068w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-1920x1920.jpeg 1920w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-50x50.jpeg 50w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-75x75.jpeg 75w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-100x100.jpeg 100w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-200x200.jpeg 200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-right-500x500.jpeg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" />
Un elemento di rilievo è la presenza di tre modalità dedicate allo sport HYROX: Allenamento, Physical Fitness Test (PFT) e Gara. Queste modalità sono studiate per rispondere alle reali esigenze degli atleti, fornendo dati dettagliati su forza, resistenza e tempi di recupero, permettendo un’analisi approfondita delle prestazioni e un miglioramento continuo.
<img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1431548" title="macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-scaled.jpeg" alt="macitynet.it" width="2560" height="2560" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-scaled.jpeg 2560w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-480x480.jpeg 480w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-1200x1200.jpeg 1200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-360x360.jpeg 360w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-1536x1536.jpeg 1536w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-2048x2048.jpeg 2048w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-420x420.jpeg 420w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-696x696.jpeg 696w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-1068x1068.jpeg 1068w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-1920x1920.jpeg 1920w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-50x50.jpeg 50w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-75x75.jpeg 75w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-100x100.jpeg 100w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-200x200.jpeg 200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Balance-2-XT-left-500x500.jpeg 500w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" />
Non manca nemmeno la modalità dedicata al padel, sport in crescita in Italia, che registra ogni colpo – da dritti a rovesci – analizzando intensità e numero degli scambi. Questa funzionalità è utile sia per i principianti che vogliono migliorare sia per i giocatori più esperti che desiderano perfezionare la tecnica e la resistenza.
Lo smartwatch è già disponibile a 199,90 euro. Tuti i prodotti del brand sono disponibili su Amazon a partire da questa vetrina. Per tutte le notizie che ruotano attorno al brand Amazfit, invece, il link da seguire è direttamente questo.

